<div>OK up to level 22 or so.  <br />
<br />
Freemarch quest chain was excellent.  The Iron Fortress was amazing.  I was so enamored of the zone that I went did every quest I could find.  <br />
<br />
The Iron Tombs are the best newbie dungeon I have ever done.  Perfectly balanced and cool event/bosses.  Wonderful atmosphere.  Tanking is a bit rough for me so far as I am still playing with my spec and have not had too many chances to tank in the past few years. <br />
<br />
Rift events, particularly in a good guild, are a total blast.  I love working with some random people to free a town from an invasion base.  It's just cool that the world changes and you have to unchange it.  <br />
<br />
This is a great game.</div>

 
